STEP|9|**src/api/routes.py:112** — No rate limiting on login endpoint.
STEP|10|**src/utils/helpers.py:8** — Duplicates logic in `src/core/utils.py:34`. Consolidate.
STEP|11|**tests/test_auth.py** — Missing edge case: expired token test.
STEP|12|Clean separation of concerns in the middleware layer
STEP|13|Good test coverage for the happy path
